            . I am a <rs id="t18191027-108-viclabel588" type="occupation">labourer</rs>
                  <join result="persNameOccupation" targOrder="Y" targets="t18191027-108-victim1167 t18191027-108-viclabel588"></join>, and live at Brompton. On the 5th of October I left a bundle, containing these things, at the bar of the <placeName id="t18191027-108-crimeloc589">Marquis of Granby, public-house</placeName>
                  <interp inst="t18191027-108-crimeloc589" type="placeName" value="Marquis of Granby, public-house"></interp>
